This paper is about generating synthetic images for training object detectors, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques to improve the performance of object detectors, which suggests that it could also be classified under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of 3D models and rendering parameters, which could be relevant to graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO).
